            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Exomni Macrini Rustici fili hic Bri<lb break="no" n="3"/>gantione geniti annorum XVI in studi<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/>valle Poenina vita functi reliquis eiu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">huc</supplied> delatis Nigria Marca mater fili<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">pient</supplied>issimo et sibi viva faciendum <lb n="7"/>curavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Brigantio named here is not Briançon, in Cottian Alps, but another place in Tarentaise with the same name. (B): Howald - Meyer: Z. 6: [kar]issimo.</p>
            </div>
